OOC: Ah, Marauder could be detecting Talon, but it seems like she should
have a Maximal signature now.  The other minions have left the base on their
own.

"It appears that the minions have left." Perseus said into the radio.
"Although they are our enemy, we can't afford a fight right now.  Team,
let's secure the rest of the base.  We don't want any surprises."

Ravenchief returned to the group and they began walking down into the base.
The area was much easier to navigate now that the lights were on, however
the place was still somewhat dark and gloomy.


On Mar 25, 2010 5:25 PM, "Preston Carroll" <supercyclonus@...> wrote:

Legacy continued for a moment, examining the strange scans from
Marauder, his single optic pulsing as he watched the information
scroll across his screen.

"Lord Perseus." Legacy intoned over the Maximal frequency, "What is to
be the disposition of the other Minion that we still have in custody.
No doubt at some point Marauder will return to reacquire his soldier."

Legacy turned to Talon, "What is the intruder's status?"
